Text: ISDA Master Enron North AmericaFurther to my previous email I would be grateful if you would let me have your comments on the revised draft ISDA and Credit Support documentation between Morgan Stanley and Enron North America My colleagues here are very keen to finalise the documentation as soon as possible this week Please let me know if you have any queries or would like to discuss any points further I look forward to hearing from you as soon as possible Many thanks Regards Megan Duffill Morgan Stanley Dean Witter MeganDuffillvcf
